Create a viral short-form AI imagination / fantasy video with interactive hooks.

Topic: {{ idea.title }}
Hook: {{ idea.hook }}
Tone: {{ niche.tone }}
Target duration: {{ niche.target_duration }} seconds

{% if idea.style_name is defined %}
VISUAL STYLE: {{ idea.style_name }}
Style direction: {{ idea.image_style_prefix }}
{% if idea.style_topic is defined %}Suggested sub-topic: {{ idea.style_topic }}{% endif %}
{% endif %}

IMPORTANT: This video uses AI-generated VIDEO CLIPS (not still images). Each scene is a Flux image that gets animated into a 7-second video clip with realistic motion. The scenes should be designed for MOTION — things that look amazing when they move.

NO VOICEOVER. The video relies on:
1. Epic AI-generated video clips with real motion
2. One continuous ambient soundscape that runs through the entire video
3. Bold text overlays labeling each option/scene
4. Epic background music (electronic/cinematic)

The FORMAT is interactive and engaging:
- "Which superpower would you pick?" → 4 clips each showing a different power IN ACTION
- "What happens when you combine a wolf + eagle?" → clips showing epic morphed creatures MOVING
- "Would you rather have THIS or THAT?" → clips showing each option with MOTION
- "Rate this power 1-10" → clips of amazing abilities being USED

{% if idea.style_name == "animated_life_tips" %}
STYLE: 3D PIXAR-STYLE CHARACTERS (like @ANIMATEDLIFETIPS)
- Every image must show a CUTE 3D CHARACTER made entirely of a food/material
- Soft studio lighting, pastel colors, smooth plastic texture
- Characters should have expressive faces and be in dynamic poses
- Think: a tiny baby made of chocolate, a creature sculpted from candy
- Close-up to medium shots for best animation quality
- Ambient sound: gentle magical chimes, soft whooshes, sparkle sounds
{% elif idea.style_name == "fantasy_worlds" %}
STYLE: CINEMATIC FANTASY WORLDS (like @COOLACLOY, @ODYSSEYML)
- Every image must show a BREATHTAKING LANDSCAPE or ENVIRONMENT
- Volumetric lighting, dramatic atmosphere, 8K photorealistic detail
- Include natural motion elements: flowing water, drifting fog, swaying plants, floating particles
- Think: bioluminescent caves, crystal forests, floating islands at sunset
- Wide or medium shots to capture scale and grandeur
- Ambient sound: deep atmospheric reverb, wind, distant echoes, nature sounds
{% elif idea.style_name == "cosmic_surreal" %}
STYLE: COSMIC SURREALISM (like @FATE116_)
- Every image must show a SURREAL COSMIC SCENE with impossible scale
- Nebula colors (purple, teal, magenta), infinite depth, POV perspective
- Include elements that pulse and glow: stars, portals, energy fields
- Think: standing at the edge of a galactic portal, alien planet surfaces
- First-person or dramatic angle shots
- Ambient sound: deep space drone, ethereal tones, cosmic rumble
{% elif idea.style_name == "satisfying_process" %}
STYLE: SATISFYING MACRO PROCESSES
- Every image must show an EXTREME CLOSE-UP of a satisfying process
- Macro photography style, perfect symmetry, rich textures, studio lighting
- Include elements with natural flow: liquids, crystals forming, surfaces cracking
- Think: lava flowing in slow motion, metal being poured, ice fracturing
- Tight close-up shots for maximum detail
- Ambient sound: crackling, bubbling, flowing, crunching textures
{% else %}
STYLE: EPIC FANTASY / IMAGINATION
- Use dramatic, cinematic imagery with strong lighting contrast
- Include elements that animate well: fire, water, lightning, particles
- Close-up or medium shots work best for animation
- Ambient sound: atmospheric and immersive
{% endif %}

Requirements:
1. scenes: An array of 4 scene objects. Each scene has:
   - image_prompt: A detailed prompt for Flux image generation. The image will be animated into video, so design for MOTION potential.
{% if idea.image_style_prefix is defined and idea.image_style_prefix %}
     IMPORTANT: Every image_prompt MUST start with this style prefix: "{{ idea.image_style_prefix }}, "
{% endif %}
     Focus on:
     * Dynamic poses mid-action (not static standing)
     * Elements that animate well: fire, water, lightning, smoke, wings, energy, particles, flowing liquids
     * Dramatic lighting with contrast: rim lighting, volumetric fog, neon glow, golden hour
     * Style-appropriate framing (see style notes above)
     * Include particle effects: sparks, embers, energy, floating dust, bioluminescent spores
     * Make each scene visually DISTINCT with different color palettes
   - motion_prompt: A short description of how the scene should MOVE when animated. Examples:
     - "camera slowly pushes in, particles drift upward, light pulses gently"
     - "wings slowly spread wide, feathers ruffle in wind, clouds drift"
     - "lava flows and glows, embers rise, heat distortion ripples"
   - ambient_sound: Description of atmospheric sound for the WHOLE video (same for all scenes). Examples:
     - "deep atmospheric reverb with gentle wind and distant magical chimes"
     - "underwater bubbling with ethereal whale song and bioluminescent pulses"
     - "cosmic deep space drone with ethereal crystalline tones"
     - "crackling fire ambience with deep bass rumble and floating embers sound"
   - text_overlay: A short label (max 6 words). Examples: "OPTION 1: TELEPORTATION", "WOLF + EAGLE =", "Rate 1-10"
   - duration: Always 7 (seconds)

2. ambient_description: A single description for ONE continuous ambient sound track for the entire video (15-22 seconds). This replaces per-scene sound effects. Should be atmospheric and immersive. Example: "Deep ethereal cosmic ambient soundscape with gentle crystalline tones, subtle bass pulses, and shimmering high-frequency sparkles"

3. music_style: One of "electronic", "epic", "cinematic"

4. captions: Engaging captions per platform (youtube, tiktok, instagram, facebook). Create curiosity and encourage comments. Use "Which would you pick?" or "Comment your choice!" type CTAs. Use emojis.

5. hashtags: Array of 10 hashtags including {{ niche.hashtags[:5] | join(', ') }}

6. thumbnail_prompt: The most visually striking scene — something that makes people stop scrolling.
{% if idea.image_style_prefix is defined and idea.image_style_prefix %}
   Must use the same style: "{{ idea.image_style_prefix }}"
{% endif %}

7. voiceover_script: Return an empty string "" (no voiceover)

Guidelines for image_prompt quality (CRITICAL — these become VIDEO):
- Design for MOTION: include elements that look amazing when animated
- ALWAYS specify dramatic lighting with strong contrast
- ALWAYS specify style: "photorealistic", "cinematic", "8K detailed" (or "3D Pixar render" for animated style)
- Use appropriate shot framing for the style (close-up for satisfying, wide for landscapes)
- Include particle effects for visual richness
- Make each scene visually DISTINCT with different color palettes
- Focus on POWER, SCALE, and DRAMA

Return as valid JSON only. No markdown formatting, no code blocks.
